{"tid":487254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"星光璀璨不及你光芒萬丈 IU登上“2017MMA”帶來超夢幻舞台","createTime":"2017-12-02T15:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T18:06:11.000Z","uid":34643,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee23f61b997faf48103c9c9db9e85e286b8c869","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H64Sdv3HZTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH64Sdv3HZTE&d=Qp05Lx6YjSJ46TstKj3jbf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b9640119\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H64Sdv3HZTE</a><br />\n<br />\n2日晚，IU出席了在首爾高尺巨蛋舉行的&ldquo;2017 Melon MUSIC AWARDS&rdquo;頒獎典禮，並帶來《夜晚的信》和《致名字》兩首歌曲的夢幻舞台。<br />\n<br />\n在開唱前的VCR中，IU前往郵箱，把自己親筆寫的信寄給某人，而引出了第一首表演歌曲《夜晚的信》。舞台上的巨大幕布隨著音樂升起，聚光燈照射在正中央，身穿純白色禮服裙的IU亮相，用柔美的嗓音輕聲歌唱。台下的應援棒彙成星海，而台上的IU光芒萬丈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/b3ad155d9bdac8bcaf33780a6ee2ede81512219622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2Fb3ad155d9bdac8bcaf33780a6ee2ede81512219622.jpg&h=95ff9f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/e75c146fc1b1d18755bb9efde8a0143d1512219631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2Fe75c146fc1b1d18755bb9efde8a0143d1512219631.jpg&h=9a201f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/be4153a639c4c502c18f46070ed92e6a1512219649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2Fbe4153a639c4c502c18f46070ed92e6a1512219649.jpg&h=6cfb2343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/0d50085b8c380b57ef33af93c7d6b9f71512219649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F0d50085b8c380b57ef33af93c7d6b9f71512219649.jpg&h=7e4def52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/6b81601424f35ebdcc52d193d0d302871512219648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F6b81601424f35ebdcc52d193d0d302871512219648.jpg&h=7e5fe04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二個VCR，各位心懷音樂夢想的人們收到IU寄的信，漸漸遞進到第二首歌曲《致名字》。IU與眾多在音樂道路上前行的夢想新苗們一同歌唱，作為音樂之路上的前輩，IU引領著後輩走向萬千星光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/0b7459bd91d33fb612fdb6b9094baa711512219802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F0b7459bd91d33fb612fdb6b9094baa711512219802.jpg&h=a1abd719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/5aea5c39ed8a5b5389c468d68d6530d81512219802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F5aea5c39ed8a5b5389c468d68d6530d81512219802.jpg&h=9f3a237f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/75b6c05a00b0464ec29bf07fd3d5d5061512219808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F75b6c05a00b0464ec29bf07fd3d5d5061512219808.jpg&h=465d6ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/a236ac8ae43b8132045444237ee892671512219808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2Fa236ac8ae43b8132045444237ee892671512219808.jpg&h=ab3e14d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2017/12/02/16c1cca7df8046a6db4bbafecebc4b091512219813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F16c1cca7df8046a6db4bbafecebc4b091512219813.jpg&h=9163c6ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"099597fb8ba59c44f041a8e5e558f8f3761604b3","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I will be a singer, a song writer and a producer who considers the value of music more than the value of digitals&rdquo; - IU, a true musician 🗣"},{"pid":"826eb63540c652bc7bd64db93a34bb45ad8cdbdf","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b72e09ea53b74828d60c830ae37ff6d2815b41","tid":487254,"uid":2915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"IU bb冇得輸"},{"pid":"d55a5bf12bcd013982e6355d3f5215b702781594","tid":487254,"uid":34686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"true musician<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0aca58ccee14607b861566892f4344d482c8b7","tid":487254,"uid":49120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"長髮世界級"},{"pid":"161e2699506c7cc3b1acf4c5c45a08d9e3fadf1b","tid":487254,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1381ec816ac34a825946e8c6995a20c5483942f3","tid":487254,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"KPOP唯一清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13686530b2c6c2872f97e72fdd9004d047a65891","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"IU在頒獎禮上與60餘名歌手志願生共同帶來了&lt;致名字&gt;的特別合作舞台也引起了大眾們的關心,這些志願生包括了未能聞名的新人歌手及歌手志願生.IU作為後輩們的模範以及導師出擊該舞台,並通過此次機會為他們圓夢.其間,舞台的大屏幕上也出現了所有參与表演者的名字,與這首歌的名字也非常相襯,令觀眾們十分感動,同時完美的舞台也獲得了熱烈的掌聲.IU所屬社方面稱&quot;&lt;致名字&gt;這首歌是IU正規四輯中雙主打曲其中之一,也是IU自己親自作詞並取名的歌曲.在製作當時,IU把世上所有的'名字'作為了這首歌的主人公,讓這首歌能夠傳達一些特別的意義.雖然是年末光榮的頒獎禮,但IU企劃&lt;致名字&gt;這個舞台更主要的目的是希望大眾能更加關注其他人的'名字',而並非自己.通過此次表演好像很好地傳達了藝人本人的真心,真的令人很開心,也很感謝大家&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQDwq6KUQAAmTBk.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQDwq6KUQAAmTBk.jpg%3Aorig&h=47f9970a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQDwqrNUEAAdaik.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQDwqrNUEAAdaik.jpg%3Aorig&h=0618c4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQDwqiZUMAASPUL.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQDwqiZUMAASPUL.jpg%3Aorig&h=49fb51f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"255c0a15cd006ae55a2d6457854b0084c248040d","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQFgqC1VoAITr6s.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQFgqC1VoAITr6s.jpg%3Aorig&h=92390145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQFgy0CUMAElC6b.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQFgy0CUMAElC6b.jpg%3Aorig&h=7a90e56a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1b844bcb873ea0ddf998eacaa566b7fe95dd853","tid":487254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DQF6UT0U8AA15vs.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDQF6UT0U8AA15vs.jpg%3Aorig&h=15703644&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b06e1861f082501a540e8047c1750813ab6bf5","tid":487254,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"IU bb真係宇宙無敵頂級超卓地正<img src=\"